functionality:
key 1: point mode
key 2: line mode
key 3: triangle mode
key 4: smooth mode
key 5: lines on top of triangles (Extra Credit)

Extra Credit:
Render wireframe on top of solid triangles (use glPolygonOffset to avoid z-buffer fighting).
this program can render pictures other than the ones are initially given.
See screenshot I have made some interesting one!!! Mario, Moon, humanface.

key k : start recording mode
key c : end recording mode
key T (hold and drag the mouse) : translate mode
key t (hold and drag the mouse) : translate mode 
key Shift(hold and drag the mouse) : scale mode
default mode(drag the mouse) : rotate mode

